<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Pet Shop</title>

    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #fef6e4;
        }

        header {
            background-color: #ff8ba7;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        nav {
            background-color: #ffc6c7;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        nav a {
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        nav a:hover {
            color: #ff8ba7;
        }

        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 42px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .hero p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background-color: #ff8ba7;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background-color: #ff6f91;
        }

        .section {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .cards {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .card {
            background: white;
            margin: 15px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 250px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        }

        footer {
            background-color: #ff8ba7;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>🐾 Welcome to My Pet Shop</h1>
    <p>Your one-stop place for happy and healthy pets!</p>
</header>

<nav>
    <a href="#">Home</a>
    <a href="#">Pets</a>
    <a href="#">Products</a>
    <a href="#">Contact</a>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
    <h1>Find Your Perfect Companion</h1>
    <p>We offer a variety of pets and supplies for your lovely friends.</p>
    <a href="#" class="btn">Shop Now</a>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Our Pets</h2>
    <div class="cards">
        <div class="card">
            <h3>🐶 Dogs</h3>
            <p>Loyal and friendly companions.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>🐱 Cats</h3>
            <p>Playful and adorable pets.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <h3>🐦 Birds</h3>
            <p>Colorful and cheerful friends.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
    <h2>Why Choose Us?</h2>
    <p>✔ Healthy pets<br>✔ Affordable prices<br>✔ Friendly service</p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 My Pet Shop | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
